The foreign policy objectives shall be-promotion and protection of the national interest;Regional group(s)promotion of African integration and support for African unity;promotion of international co-operation for the consolidation of universal peace and mutual respect among all nations and elimination of discrimination in all its manifestations;International lawrespect for international law and treaty obligations as well as the seeking of settlement of international disputes by negotiation, mediation, conciliation, arbitration and adjudication; andpromotion of a just world economic order.
